      section.bordered(data-name='overlay')
        h2 Overlays
        p Overlays are like dialog boxes.
        p
          | Supported classes: <code>.from-top</code>, <code>.from-bottom</code> and <code>.floating</code>.
          | <code>.from-top</code> will come down from the top of the UI, etc.


        .overlay.from-top
          div Some content


      section.bordered(data-name='select-list')
        h2 Select List


        p This is how you will typically specify a <code>.select-list</code>.

        p The list items have many options you can use, and shows you how they will display.

        h3 Basic example with one item.selected

        .overlay.from-top.select-list
          input.editor.editor-colors.mini
          ol.list-group
            li.selected
              span one
            li two
            li three


        h3 Single line with icons

        .overlay.from-top.select-list
          ol.list-group
            li.selected
              .status.status-added.icon.icon-diff-added
              .icon.icon-file-text Some file
            li
                .status.status-modified.icon.icon-diff-modified
                .icon.icon-file-text.Another.file
              li
                .status.status-removed.icon.icon-diff-removed
                .icon.icon-file-text.Yet.another.file


        h3 Multiple lines with no icons

        .overlay.from-top.select-list
          ol.list-group
            li.two-lines
              .primary-line Primary line
              .secondary-line Secondary line
            li.two-lines.selected
                .primary-line A thing
                .secondary-line Description of the thing


        h3 Multiple lines with icons

        .overlay.from-top.select-list
          .list-group
            .two-lines
              .status.status-added.icon.icon-diff-added
              .primary-line.icon.icon-file-text Primary line
              .secondary-line.no-icon Secondary line
              .two-lines.selected
                .status.status-modified.icon.icon-diff-modified
                .primary-line.icon.icon-file-symlink-file A thing
                .secondary-line.no-icon Description of the thing
              .two-lines
                .status.status-renamed.icon.icon-diff-renamed
                .primary-line.icon.icon-file-symlink-file A thing
                .secondary-line.no-icon Description of the thing


        h3 Using mark.selected class to indicate the.selected item
        p Use ...

        .overlay.from-top.select-list
          ol.list-group.mark.selected
            li Normal item
            li.selected Selected &mdash; user is arrowing through the list.
            li.active This is the active item
            li.selected.active Selected AND active!


        h3 Error messages
        .example-rendered
          .overlay.from-top.select-list
            .editor.editor-colors.mini I searched for this
            .error-message Nothing has been found!


        h3 Loading message

        .overlay.from-top.select-list
          .editor.editor-colors.mini User input
          .loading
            .loading-message Chill bro. Things are loading.
            .badge 1234


